Paper: hep-th/9401168

Date: 1994-01-31

Title: The Number Operator for Generalized Quons

Authors: Miroslav Doresic

Comments: 12 pages , Latex, ( final version )

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A28 (1995) 189-196

We construct the number operator for particles obeying infinite statistics,defined by a generalized q-deformation of the Heisenberg algebra, and prove thepositivity of the norm of linearly independent state vectors.